 [October 1917] Oct 1st 1917 . Woke about 10 o,clock this morn after a real good snore , had a good scrub down in a shell hole veri refresh . We move off again about 3P.M and reach " Halifax Camp " at 6 o,clock . Enemi plane over to night bomb , some fell veri close to our camp , sever hors kill , and other damag done . 2nd " Fritz " plane over earli this morn drop bomb , sever casualti . Anti-Aircraft gun veri busi tri to bring them down , also Machin gun blaze away . 11th Oct. 33 Year of age to day still go strong .
